title: Tues Post Show (06-21-22)

description:
We get an update on the Best Childhood Snack Draft and find out who has to suck their thumb and post a picture on Instagram. Lunchbox is upset at Eddie stealing his name, image and likeness. Bobby talks about getting hate from his picture from dinner last night. Raymundo has another country music secret. Bobby’s wife called out Eddie who was watching UFC at his comedy show over the weekend.
